---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="about — corb.cc">
  <section class="page-intro">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">about</p>
      <h1>hi, i’m corbin</h1>

      <p class="intro">
        I’m a photographer, videographer, and someone who cares a lot about
        how things feel. Most of what I make lives somewhere between
        documentation and expression.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="side-note">
      <p>rexburg / idaho</p>
      <p>photos / video / teaching</p>
      <p>climbing / media / internet</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="rule dashed"></div>

  <section class="about-body">
    <div class="about-main">
      <p>
        I started with photography, mostly because I liked the idea of
        capturing something before it disappeared. Over time, that turned
        into video, editing, and trying to understand why certain things
        feel meaningful.
      </p>

      <p>
        A lot of my work is split between client work and personal projects.
        I like both for different reasons. Client work lets me show up for
        people and make something that matters to them. Personal work lets me
        explore things I don’t fully understand yet.
      </p>

      <p>
        This site is meant to hold everything in one place. Not just finished
        work, but ideas, experiments, and things that don’t really have a
        category yet.
      </p>

      <p>
        I care a lot about making things that feel honest. Even if they’re
        simple. Even if they’re unfinished.
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="about-side">
      <p class="section-label">currently</p>
      <ul>
        <li>editing video projects</li>
        <li>shooting weddings + portraits</li>
        <li>finishing this website</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="section-label">influences</p>
      <ul>
        <li>games / old tech</li>
        <li>film + video essays</li>
        <li>early internet culture</li>
        <li>idk</li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <div class="rule"></div>

  <section class="about-footer">
    <p>
      if you made it this far, thanks for being here.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-intro {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 1.8rem 0 1.4rem;
    align-items: end;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .intro {
    max-width: 38rem;
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .side-note {
    justify-self: end;
    text-align: right;
    color: var(--soft);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .side-note p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 1.6rem 0;
  }

  .about-main p {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 42rem;
  }

  .about-side ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 1.4rem;
  }

  .about-side li {
    margin: 0.25rem 0;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .about-footer {
    padding-top: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--soft);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .page-intro,
    .about-body {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .side-note {
      justify-self: start;
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>